{"tid":1505003,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有無人識個12歲小朋友？","createTime":"2019-08-25T12:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T18:46:29.000Z","uid":35249,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1153c8498e6dfe16fcfd363b9f0ec0a33f8bc153","tid":1505003,"uid":35249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dsM5wR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dsM5wR.jpg&h=dd67abd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星火搵緊個啱啱係荃灣楊屋道俾狗拉咗上私家車個12歲小朋友<br />\n<br />\n有無人識佢？"},{"pid":"1f550a0da230c76c79fdf2e061aded7c23a5ef30","tid":1505003,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:30:03.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"b3c0447d5ba10199a2f784f04db4fb9e22826926","tid":1505003,"uid":175091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"aeb932cccfeb5a97f94db1a1c1b34056be33215a","tid":1505003,"uid":1315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"推 國際核彈黎 一定要推上國際層面"},{"pid":"ccafa4554b1fe2d37e5789527e339a8a9b1d7ac3","tid":1505003,"uid":35249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"唔俾社工跟車"},{"pid":"bab7669265f8aa28c48c17002abbe4ad809891a2","tid":1505003,"uid":299984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:46:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2b8cb99298c59beb8ea85c3857016d3e2dda2a68","tid":1505003,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb932cccfeb5a97f94db1a1c1b34056be33215a","tid":1505003,"uid":1315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"推 國際核彈黎 一定要推上國際層面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T13:08:07.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">勇武/前線/first aid/街坊 比人爆頭.爆眼.斬斷手腳筋.昏迷黑警無即時送院.警署酷刑致骨折.爆牙咩都有</span></ins></em><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n各位鍵盤戰士/文宣/香港幫手炒輿論，<br />\n炒黑警酷刑逼認罪<br />\n炒黑警保護福建國斬人<br />\n炒黑警anti humanity, 稱呼示威者為曱甴<br />\n炒到黑警證人不可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">求下各位幫手推推<br />\n細佬p牌推唔到，希望可以<strong><ins>推到狗做唔到證人</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><ins>7百幾個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">被捕人士</span>，最細<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">12歲</span>，比人拉入警署受過咩<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">酷刑</span>，被人<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">性侵犯</span></strong>，逼簽左咩認左咩都無人知</ins></strong>，唔可以就咁算，要互幫，所以希望大家可以幫幫手，<strong><ins>炒左個輿論出黎先</ins></strong><br />\n最少佢地<strong><ins>唔會比人咁易屈襲警</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【集思廣益】&ldquo;法庭不應採立香港警方為誠實可靠證人&rdquo;聯署行動(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1494456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1494456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n[黑警] 警方終承認新屋嶺密室恐怖審問 導致31人送院6人情況嚴重（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1494263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1494263</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【國際戰線】同你班撚樣講多次，仇恨言論係鬼佬眼中非常敏感，特別係美國佬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476435</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論</ins></strong>區</span><br />\n<br />\n另外如果有巴絲知道下面單嘢可以點用就點用，炒爆垃圾監狗會<br />\n<br />\n#可怕的投訴警察課<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/714547433/posts/10155971867622434?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F714547433%2Fposts%2F10155971867622434%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp898yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=2e4d291e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/714547433/posts/10155971867622434?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"698e981e3e04e7ed721c0a399994c40dc6b33d4b","tid":1505003,"uid":272569,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb932cccfeb5a97f94db1a1c1b34056be33215a","tid":1505003,"uid":1315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T12:33:00.000Z","